      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. The dual-VANOS system has been professionally serviced, and the chassis features essential rear subframe reinforcement to maintain structural rigidity under high lateral loads. It utilizes a factory M-tuned limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution and refreshed bushings throughout the multi-link rear suspension. This is a mechanically sorted example that delivers the precise throttle response and balanced handling dynamics expected of the marque.",
